---
layout: base.njk
title: Guides
description: Setup walkthroughs, hardware notes, and reference manuals for AZOM — the MOZA bridge for SimHub.
permalink: /guides/
---
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="doc-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Documentation</p>
    <h2 class="h2">Guides &amp; manuals</h2>
    <p class="lede">Step-by-step setup, hardware-specific notes, and reference for getting AZOM running on your rig.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="guide-list">
    {% for g in collections.guides %}
    <a class="guide-card" href="{{ g.url }}">
      <div class="idx">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</div>
      <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
      <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
      <div class="go">Read →</div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>
